    "{\n",
    " \"cells\": [\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"# Text Normalization Pipeline\\n\",\"**NLP Project 17 of 100**\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Project Overview\\n\",\"Build a comprehensive text normalization pipeline: handle contractions, emojis, slang, URLs, emails, punctuation, and unicode.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Learning Objectives\\n\",\"1. Build modular text cleaning functions.\\n\",\"2. Handle real-world text noise (social media, emails, chat).\\n\",\"3. Measure normalization impact on downstream tasks.\\n\",\"\\n\",\"## Why This Matters\\n\",\"Raw text from the web contains noise that degrades NLP model performance.\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import subprocess, sys, importlib\\nfor pkg in [\\\"pandas\\\",\\\"numpy\\\",\\\"matplotlib\\\",\\\"seaborn\\\"]:\\n    try: importlib.import_module(pkg)\\n    except ImportError: subprocess.check_call([sys.executable,\\\"-m\\\",\\\"pip\\\",\\\"install\\\",\\\"-q\\\",pkg])\\nprint('Ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"import numpy as np, pandas as pd, re, unicodedata\\nimport matplotlib.pyplot as plt, seaborn as sns\\nimport warnings; warnings.filterwarnings('ignore')\\nsns.set_style('whitegrid')\\n%matplotlib inline\\nSEED = 42\\nprint('Loaded.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Normalization Functions\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"CONTRACTIONS = {\\\"can't\\\":\\\"cannot\\\",\\\"won't\\\":\\\"will not\\\",\\\"don't\\\":\\\"do not\\\",\\\"isn't\\\":\\\"is not\\\",\\n    \\\"wasn't\\\":\\\"was not\\\",\\\"aren't\\\":\\\"are not\\\",\\\"i'm\\\":\\\"i am\\\",\\\"i've\\\":\\\"i have\\\",\\n    \\\"i'll\\\":\\\"i will\\\",\\\"i'd\\\":\\\"i would\\\",\\\"he's\\\":\\\"he is\\\",\\\"she's\\\":\\\"she is\\\",\\n    \\\"it's\\\":\\\"it is\\\",\\\"we're\\\":\\\"we are\\\",\\\"they're\\\":\\\"they are\\\",\\\"you're\\\":\\\"you are\\\",\\n    \\\"that's\\\":\\\"that is\\\",\\\"there's\\\":\\\"there is\\\",\\\"couldn't\\\":\\\"could not\\\",\\n    \\\"shouldn't\\\":\\\"should not\\\",\\\"wouldn't\\\":\\\"would not\\\",\\\"haven't\\\":\\\"have not\\\",\\n    \\\"hasn't\\\":\\\"has not\\\",\\\"didn't\\\":\\\"did not\\\",\\\"doesn't\\\":\\\"does not\\\"}\\n\\ndef expand_contractions(text):\\n    for k, v in CONTRACTIONS.items():\\n        text = re.sub(r'\\\\b' + re.escape(k) + r'\\\\b', v, text, flags=re.IGNORECASE)\\n    return text\\n\\ndef remove_urls(text): return re.sub(r'https?://\\\\S+|www\\\\.\\\\S+', '', text)\\ndef remove_emails(text): return re.sub(r'\\\\S+@\\\\S+', '', text)\\ndef remove_html(text): return re.sub(r'<[^>]+>', '', text)\\ndef normalize_unicode(text): return unicodedata.normalize('NFKD', text)\\ndef remove_extra_spaces(text): return re.sub(r'\\\\s+', ' ', text).strip()\\ndef remove_emojis(text): return re.sub(r'[^\\\\w\\\\s.,!?;:\\\\'-]', '', text)\\n\\ndef normalize_text(text):\\n    text = text.lower()\\n    text = remove_html(text)\\n    text = remove_urls(text)\\n    text = remove_emails(text)\\n    text = expand_contractions(text)\\n    text = remove_emojis(text)\\n    text = normalize_unicode(text)\\n    text = remove_extra_spaces(text)\\n    return text\\n\\nprint('Functions ready.')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Test Examples\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"tests = [\\n    \\\"I can't believe it!!! 😂😂 Check https://example.com for more\\\",\\n    \\\"She's won't DON'T   extra   spaces   here\\\",\\n    \\\"Email me at test@email.com <b>HTML tags</b>\\\",\\n    \\\"I'm so happyyy 🎉🎉🎉 it's amazing!!!\\\",\\n    \\\"Won't you come to the café? It's résumé time.\\\"\\n]\\n\\nfor t in tests:\\n    print(f'Original:   {t}')\\n    print(f'Normalized: {normalize_text(t)}')\\n    print()\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Pipeline Analysis\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"code\",\"execution_count\":null,\"metadata\":{},\"outputs\":[],\"source\":[\"steps = ['Original','Lowercase','Remove URLs','Expand Contractions','Remove Emojis','Final']\\nsample = \\\"I can't believe it!!! 😂 Check https://example.com\\\"\\nstates = [sample, sample.lower(), remove_urls(sample.lower()),\\n          expand_contractions(remove_urls(sample.lower())),\\n          remove_emojis(expand_contractions(remove_urls(sample.lower()))),\\n          normalize_text(sample)]\\n\\nfor step, state in zip(steps, states):\\n    print(f'{step:22s}: {state}')\"]},\n",
    "  {\"cell_type\":\"markdown\",\"metadata\":{},\"source\":[\"## Summary\\n\",\"- **Text normalization is essential** for consistent NLP processing.\\n\",\"- **Modular pipeline design** allows easy customization per task.\\n\",\"- **Order matters**: remove HTML before URLs, expand contractions before tokenization.\\n\",\"- **For production, use spaCy or custom preprocessing** with domain-specific rules.\"]}\n",
    " ],\n",
